name: Oracles of the Runic Lullaby
description: There are Rootmason carvings all over the heirlooms of the Oracles of the Runic Lullaby. Why? How? They're also known for their captivating music that seems to overwhelm listeners with ecstasy. Now biding their time as healers in nearby villages, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
